      PROCESS ARITH(COMPAT)
       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. PROCESS-ARITH-COMPAT.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-PRICE       PIC S9(5)V99.
       01  WS-QTY         PIC S9(3).
       01  WS-TOTAL       PIC S9(7)V99.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       0000-MAIN.
           MOVE 125.50 TO WS-PRICE.
           MOVE 48 TO WS-QTY.
           COMPUTE WS-TOTAL = WS-PRICE * WS-QTY.
           STOP RUN.
